You’ll see if there’s any transaction history or balance (most likely it will be empty).


⚠ Important Security Note

If this number were a real private key with funds, running this code would give you full control of that wallet.

Since it’s almost certainly a random token from Cloudflare, it should have no funds — but always treat private keys as sensitive.

